description:
The Straw Hats continue to suffer from blazing heat and a perilous food crisis! As the seas finally calm, fishing is their only hope! Meanwhile, Sanji arrives in Big Mom`s territory and keeps his cool - until he sees his bride-to-be!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Le retour de Sanji. Au beau milieu du territoire de Big Mom !
Sanji Kikyou: Big Mom no Nawabari e!
Sanji`s Homecoming! Into Big Mom`s Territory!
Sanjis Rückkehr! – Auf in Big Moms Territorium!
Санджи возвращается домой! Территория Большой Мамочки!
サンジ帰郷 ビッグ・マムの海峡[ナワバリ]へ!
